MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2001-0871. State v. Ahmed.

Belmont C.P. No. 99-CR-192. On motion for leave to amend, and on application for reopening under S.Ct.Prac.R. XI(6). Motions denied because the appellant failed to comply with the 90-day filing deadline in S.Ct.Prac.R. XI(6)(A).

Pfeifer, J., dissents.
